{"tid":46402,"cid":28,"subCid":0,"title":"公道啲講","createTime":"2016-12-19T15:34:43.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-19T17:35:01.000Z","uid":2705,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0f6306e932e50fd92f1b29debaa7b7a0a3149cce","tid":46402,"uid":2705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T15:34:43.000Z","msg":"其實個絲打用咁多心機整曬成set icon出黎，都要用好多心機同時間<br />\n<br />\n唔係叫啲唔鐘意既巴絲因為咁而硬食肥婆icon，只係覺得一樣米養百樣人，緊有人鐘意有人唔鐘意<br />\n<br />\n如果以後有巴絲整新icon出黎，一有人覺得唔順眼就係咁屌，只會屌到冇人肯整新icon<br />\n<br />\n有巴打講得好啱，而家唔係我唔鐘意就唔用咁簡單，係我唔用但係其他人用既話都要見到<br />\n<br />\n唔通要見一個block一個做到咁偏激咩<br />\n<br />\n既然有人鐘意有人唔鐘意，不如好似其他巴打話齋，整個icon filter出黎啦<br />\n<br />\n就好似block人系統咁，覺得唔順眼咪block左佢唔好見到佢囉<br />\n<br />\n最理想係可以做到：<br />\n1.) 當有人用肥婆icon果陣，係自己個app度睇既話會變做另一set icon<br />\n2.) in case黎緊越黎越多icon set果陣，可以係自己個app度更改icon set既排序<br />\n<br />\n當然而家就1.) 係重要啲既<br />\n<br />\n當初就係因為早洩唔重視user意見所以先有好多巴絲轉左會過黎，所以希望admin們可以搵到個方案係兩邊巴絲都滿意，咁樣先可以留住巴絲。<br />\n<br />\n最後，如果各位巴絲認為filter係work既就留個名推post比admin們見到啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：唔鐘意肥婆icon<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c724b357b722cb635dccab14c00df7ecdf961318","tid":46402,"uid":2705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T15:41:00.000Z","msg":"自推一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee0b3da9cf70617676ccb7fc982b0241e4188fe1","tid":46402,"uid":51129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T16:20:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07a49ae8c07d974fc221d521c8c7033def02f919","tid":46402,"uid":51250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T16:37:23.000Z","msg":"加埋d低能icon搞到好似babykingdom discuss咁，弱撚智"},{"pid":"aed64636288cc3c4dcc88926a280398ecf01b830","tid":46402,"uid":2126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T16:55:34.000Z","msg":"淨係「絲打出品」已經出晒水啦, 係咪?"},{"pid":"886fb9b6349d6a5c8fe00c9c5d7c043fc4fde0e3","tid":46402,"uid":46507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T16:57:40.000Z","msg":"自家製係值得欣賞 , <br />\n但真係好柒 , sorry頂唔順"},{"pid":"f6ec10ae94d6124b0518c6ad9d0301492d23baf9","tid":46402,"uid":34444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T17:03:33.000Z","msg":"遲撚早變到line咁十鳩幾廿萬款野比人用 唔止得肥婆<br />\n應盡早阻止咪撚搞臭個壇"},{"pid":"2bb406b4f9c4100a4710d9a107beb25869bff267","tid":46402,"uid":24455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T17:11:24.000Z","msg":"做設計一開始唔體會用家意見<br />\n自己埋頭苦幹一番後至拎去比顧客試用<br />\n係死罪"},{"pid":"9991f69d79cfaf22e77b7806e828a37b5edaa4d2","tid":46402,"uid":31423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T17:13:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>淨係「絲打出品」已經出晒水啦, 係咪?</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b79582bc090c573bef2d71d4989a36aff18f36f7","tid":46402,"uid":1049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T17:16:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔會block,我會屌全世界要全世界就我<br />\n但我會自己搵自已生存空間<br />\n道不同不相為謀，當初早洩bam hkg+逼我黎呢度，今日係撐肥婆icon既人逼我返高登，完</span>"},{"pid":"1505df581b55f598c24cba2d88443030f7ad600a","tid":46402,"uid":1049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T17:16:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔會block,我唔會屌全世界要全世界就我<br />\n但我會自己搵自已生存空間<br />\n道不同不相為謀，當初早洩bam hkg+逼我黎呢度，今日係撐肥婆icon既人逼我返高登，完</span></blockquote>"},{"pid":"403f8179979eb1223fa6d1d223dbcbbad3fdeb0d","tid":46402,"uid":51250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T17:35:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}